column5: Something wrong with the world today, The light bulb is getting dim.  Just have to live on the edge and get it done.

How do you post the vid where the picture of it shows up not just the blue link.  On Youtube copy the embed code and on the reply to topic click on more reply options and then on the right side enable HTML. Paste code into window and you're good to go.
